Was laughing pretty hard at some of the scenes. Ended, for now, only Alex's route (going for Ian's and Jed's) with all CGs, but HECK this was an adventure! Cute and awesome game for evening meetings with "friend" and wine.
- I'm totally in love with the art, men in general and face expressions are drawn super professional and perfect;
- The theme in main menu is so good, it stuck in my head for long;
- CGs are like commisioned arts, they are worth collecting;
- We have like the best friends in game, and in general VNs categories, I want such roomates in my life too;
- Also the stories of guys are so well written (pretty time-taking too!), every one of them is unique and with his own flaws and beautiful character features. Maybe sometimes you get the "stereotypical" feeling of some texts, but it's just sometimes.
It lacks voice-over which is a shame for such a good game, I wanted to hear Penny, Ian and Alex  what they might sound like. BUT, I accidentally hit "V" button which affects in many laughs - I don't know if it is choose by country, but Polish one was so hilarious! Please... Just do it.

In general, really awesome game for adults with interesting story and characters - and I think I would not take it back!
P.S. Wonderful easter-egg with Tycho Minogue! :)
